



Gentn
Williamsburg Novr 20th 1772



By some kind of mismanagement Seven Hogsheads of Mr Custiss Tobacco (from the Plantation on the Eastern Shore) missed a Passage in Captain Peterson; and Insurance made for that many more than the Ship carried of his, which you will please to have rectified, as I knew nothing of the disappointment till I came to this place a few days ago1I have drawn two Bills upon you of this date in favour of [      ] for One hundred and fifty and Two hundred and fifty pounds Sterling which
[128]
please to pay and place to Mr Custiss2 and you will thereby oblige Gentn Yr Most Hble Servt

Go: Washington

